title: Episode #15: Man Stories with Kasper
description: Welcome back to another edition of the Art of Manliness podcast. This week we return to our series called Man Stories where we interview a different gentleman and ask him what it means to be a man. This week our guest is Kasper from London, England. Thanks, Kasper!
author: contact@artofmanliness.com (The Art of Manliness)
